id":1543913,"uid":51037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"不篤灰..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8336de0d0f8c916d05a5703e6ad1cee6e143825","tid":1543913,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"上個星期陪呀嘛落去諗住拎返幾枝豉油啦，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢見我咁後生又着黑衫，二話不說就塞咗成皮嘢落我褲袋，話係之前行完未找數俾班兄弟，仲話上兩個禮拜上咗北京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以拖咁耐<br />\n<br />\n跟住再搵個姐仔使開我呀嫲，靜靜雞帶我去後門個倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我驚啦諗住叫唔好，點知原來個倉入邊，成個軍火庫嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係有真槍子彈，不過隻鐵架擺咗上百枝雞尾酒嘩，仲有幾座啲小型投石器小型弩砲咁樣嘅裝置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />funfun仲話喎，佢同啲科學家喺北京實測過，一定射程遠果popo啲玩具槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫我同班fd溝通好，下次上堂記得入去搵佢借文具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過吖，大佬我淨係諗住落嚟攞枝豉油返屋企炒餸咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbf111b1f887ba2f714604a0748d911759d926d","tid":1543913,"uid":267630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:53:32.000Z","msg":"見佢自爆我先敢講, 其實早響6月已經見過佢<br />\n<br />\n佢上晒gear, 攞住成箱頭盔同眼罩, 係咁問手足要唔要<br />\n當時我好感動, 阿嬸都企到咁前<br />\n直至佢除口罩飲水, 我先知原來係梁美芬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢以為哩響暗角飲水冇人見到, 其實我一直都望住<br />\n<br />\n真係多謝佢!!"},{"pid":"dcf2f6af8df8a9ae279f477759f3bd336c462464","tid":1543913,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:18:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5zuyVClOmZE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5zuyVClOmZE&d=g6cJ